{"tid":2173214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲禁止蒙牛收購奶品公司「Lion-Dairy & Drinks」，力保澳洲奶業金漆招牌","createTime":"2020-08-25T05:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T08:55:30.000Z","uid":48040,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d9563f980e783e585d2fe247da42a763e744a36d","tid":2173214,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"由於中國、澳洲關係緊張，中國乳製品巨頭蒙牛乳業（Mengniu Dairy）收購日本麒麟控股（Kirin Holdings）所有的、總部位於墨爾本乳品公司「Lion-Dairy &amp; Drinks」的交易案告吹。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報導，2家公司去年11月達成協議，蒙牛乳業以約456億日圓（約新台幣126.5億元）的價格收購Lion-Dairy &amp; Drinks業務，但澳洲財長佛萊登柏格（Josh Frydenberg）反對。<br />\n<br />\n2家公司分別在各自聲明中表示，由於尚未獲得監管部門的批准，他們同意終止交易。<br />\n<br />\n中、澳的緊張關係近期浮現，澳洲祭出許多回應，諸如禁止華為參與5G網路、呼籲獨立調查武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）爆發起源等等。中國也憤怒回擊，停止進口部分澳洲牛肉、加徵大麥關稅，並正調查澳洲紅酒是否反傾銷，此外也警告中國公民於澳洲留學的風險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3270414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3270414&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=2a89ad9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3270414&h=b300bb0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3270414</a>"},{"pid":"a845b388083c1ca6a18d5be95c5fa89f1660ae25","tid":2173214,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2ea50739883a9f9ce43ff65f8f8e034632b9be","tid":2173214,"uid":48040,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"一粒老鼠屎，搞禍一鍋粥。"},{"pid":"b4609dc81345b9f253dd090b6cd74663c6fc09a4","tid":2173214,"uid":151074,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T06:02:48.000Z","msg":"国家係無真牛奶真橙汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass